en-CA.summary: The classic childhood game of kill bang marry has come to alexa.
en-CA.name: Kill Bang Marry Game
en-CA.description: There are two parts to this skill. One where you can give Alexa 3 names and she will choose who to kill, bang and marry. Part two is where you can choose from a variety of preset categories and Alexa will give you 3 names to play with.
